title: D90GUIDE100.pdf
description: The Complete Guide to the Nikon D90 1st Edition: this 800+ page eBook (PDF file) contains everything you'd want to know about the D90 and how to use it, including how to use it as a video camera. You'll find deep explanations with more examples and suggestions than in previous and other guides, all in the no-nonsense and understandable writing style for which Thom Hogan has become famous. No matter how well you think you know the D90, you'll find things in this work that you didn't know about the camera (try pressing the OK button twice while reviewing an image; surprised?). That's why it's called a "complete guide."
